				<div id="head-tag">	




	
				


	
				
																					

				
	</div>
				<h1 id="headline" class="eza-title">
											
What happens to rule of law if the law keeps changing?									</h1>
			</div>
		</div>

		
				<div class="row">
			<div class="editor-intro small-centered eza-body small-12 medium-11">
				<h2 class="title text-center">Why We Wrote This</h2>
				<div>
					
<p>Interpretations of law change over time, of course. But a case before the U.S. Supreme Court highlights what can happen when politics flip-flop so wildly and quickly.</p>				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				<article id="story-content">
			
